com.interpss.core.aclf.hvdc

Interface BaseVSCConverter<TBus extends BaseAclfBus<?,?>>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BusRef<TBus>, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    VSCConverter, VSCConverterDyn
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseVSCConverterImpl, VSCConverterDynImpl, VSCConverterImpl

    public interface BaseVSCConverter<TBus extends BaseAclfBus<?,?>>
extends BusRef<TBus>
    A representation of the model object 'Base VSC Converter'. HVDC VSC Converer

    The following features are supported:

    • Vdc
    • Pdc
    • Dc Set Point
    • Ac Set Point
    • Mva Rating
    • Ac Current Rating
    • QMax Mvar
    • QMin Mvar
    • Power Into Network Mva
    • Ac Control Mode
    • Dc Control Mode
    • Remote Control Bus Id
    • Remote Control Percent
    • Rectifier
    • Parent Hvdc
    See Also:
    HvdcLinePackage.getBaseVSCConverter()
